{"meta":{"version":"121","folder":"EventFlowMsg","file":"Dm_ZE_0007","chunk":0,"start":0,"count":54,"total":54},"rows":[{"id":9118,"index":0,"key":"Dm_ZE_0007_Text_000_b","CNzh":"劳鲁陛下，","TWzh":"勞魯陛下。","JPja":"ラウル<Ruby={2:4}どの>殿","USen":"King Rauru..."},{"id":9119,"index":1,"key":"Dm_ZE_0007_Text_001_b","CNzh":"刚才的报告……\n说是格鲁德沙漠最后的村子也已经被攻陷。","TWzh":"根據剛才的報告……\n格魯德沙漠最後一個村落也已經被攻陷。","JPja":"<Ruby={2:4}さき>先ほど <Ruby={4:8}でんれい>伝令が…\nゲルド<Ruby={4:6}さばく>砂漠でも <Ruby={4:6}さいご>最後の<Ruby={2:4}むら>村が<Ruby={2:2}せ>攻め<Ruby={2:2}お>落とされたと","USen":"We just received word that the last free village\nin the Gerudo Desert has fallen."},{"id":9120,"index":2,"key":"Dm_ZE_0007_Text_001_bb","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":9121,"index":3,"key":"Dm_ZE_0007_Text_001_c","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":9122,"index":4,"key":"Dm_ZE_0007_Text_002_ab","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":9123,"index":5,"key":"Dm_ZE_0007_Text_002_b","CNzh":"这样下去就抵御不住魔王军的侵略了。","TWzh":"我們已經無法阻擋魔王軍的侵略了。","JPja":"これ<Ruby={4:8}いじょう>以上 <Ruby={6:10}まおうぐん>魔王軍の<Ruby={4:8}しんこう>侵攻を<Ruby={2:4}ふせ>防ぐことはできません","USen":"At this rate, the Demon King's army will overwhelm us."},{"id":9124,"index":6,"key":"Dm_ZE_0007_Text_003_b","CNzh":"……我明白。","TWzh":"……我明白。","JPja":"…わかっている","USen":"I understand."},{"id":9125,"index":7,"key":"Dm_ZE_0007_Text_004_b","CNzh":"我会阻止身为元凶的魔王。","TWzh":"我來阻止身為罪魁禍首的魔王。","JPja":"<Ruby={4:10}げんきょう>元凶である<Ruby={4:6}まおう>魔王は <Ruby={2:6}わたし>私が<Ruby={2:2}と>止める","USen":"Our only hope is for me to defeat the Demon King."},{"id":9126,"index":8,"key":"Dm_ZE_0007_Text_005_b","CNzh":"劳鲁，","TWzh":"勞魯。","JPja":"ラウル","USen":"Rauru."},{"id":9127,"index":9,"key":"Dm_ZE_0007_Text_006_b","CNzh":"现在的魔王，已经无法由你一人来阻止了。","TWzh":"魔王已經強大到你一個人無法阻止了。","JPja":"もはや <Ruby={4:6}まおう>魔王は <Ruby={4:6}そなた>其方<Ruby={4:6}ひとり>一人で<Ruby={2:2}と>止められるものではありません","USen":"The Demon King... He is not someone you can stop\nby yourself."},{"id":9128,"index":10,"key":"Dm_ZE_0007_Text_007_b","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":9129,"index":11,"key":"Dm_ZE_0007_Text_008_b","CNzh":"但是你并不是孤身一人。","TWzh":"但你並不是孤軍奮戰。","JPja":"しかし <Ruby={4:6}そなた>其方は<Ruby={2:4}ひと>独りではない","USen":"But...you are not alone."},{"id":9130,"index":12,"key":"Dm_ZE_0007_Text_009_b","CNzh":"你的身边有格鲁德、鼓隆、卓拉、利特的族长，还有塞尔达……","TWzh":"格魯德、鼓隆、卓拉、利特四族的族長，還有薩爾達……","JPja":"ゲルド ゴロン ゾーラ リトの<Ruby={4:10}ぞくちょう>族長に ゼルダ…","USen":"You have the Gerudo, Goron, Zora, and Rito leaders,\nas well as Zelda..."},{"id":9131,"index":13,"key":"Dm_ZE_0007_Text_009_baaab","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":9132,"index":14,"key":"Dm_ZE_0007_Text_009_baab","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":9133,"index":15,"key":"Dm_ZE_0007_Text_009_bab","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":9134,"index":16,"key":"Dm_ZE_0007_Text_009_bb","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":9135,"index":17,"key":"Dm_ZE_0007_Text_009_c","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":9136,"index":18,"key":"Dm_ZE_0007_Text_010_b","CNzh":"当然，我也会与你并肩作战……","TWzh":"然後，我當然也會與你同在……","JPja":"そして もちろん<Ruby={2:6}わたし>私もここにいる…","USen":"And of course...you can count on me."},{"id":9137,"index":19,"key":"Dm_ZE_0007_Text_011_ab","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":9138,"index":20,"key":"Dm_ZE_0007_Text_011_b","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":9139,"index":21,"key":"Dm_ZE_0007_Text_012_c","CNzh":"我有件东西想给大家看一看……","TWzh":"……我有東西想給各位看……","JPja":"… <Ruby={2:4}みな>皆に<Ruby={2:2}み>見せたいものが<Ruby={2:2}あ>在る…","USen":"There's something I'd like to show you all."},{"id":9140,"index":22,"key":"Dm_ZE_0007_Text_013_b","CNzh":"这是左纳乌的……","TWzh":"左納烏的……","JPja":"ゾナウの…","USen":"Zonai..."},{"id":9141,"index":23,"key":"Dm_ZE_0007_Text_014_b","CNzh":"秘石……","TWzh":"秘石……","JPja":"<Ruby={4:6}ひせき>秘石…","USen":"Secret stones..."},{"id":9142,"index":24,"key":"Dm_ZE_0007_Text_015_ab","CNzh":"","TWzh":"","JPja":"","USen":""},{"id":9143,"index":25,"key":"Dm_ZE_0007_Text_015_c","CNzh":"请大家借与我力量。","TWzh":"請各位助我一臂之力。","JPja":"<Ruby={2:4}みな>皆の<Ruby={2:6}ちから>力を <Ruby={2:6}わた